The paper deals with enhancing machine learning systems through a hierarchical approach to generate abstract context representations. This involves natural language processing and neural networks, which are typically associated with the computer science sub-categories of Computational Linguistics (cs.CL), Machine Learning (cs.LG), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE), and Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition (cs.CV). Therefore, these are the most likely sub-categories for this paper, with cs.CL being the most likely due to the focus on natural language processing.
